title: i am trying to find someone in oce sever
body: i am trying to find a gangplank main in silver/gold and urgot main name start with N in silver/gold in oce sever , if u have seen them plz tell me :)

replies.body: Amm I remember this gangplank main said this to me :"gangplank = freelo"

Hey U mOthEr FckeR,

That's extremely vague and you'll never find them that way. If you played a match with them before you can go through your match history and look for them. I'd open your [**op.gg profile**](http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=U%20mOthEr%20FckeR) and just start looking for Urgots and Gangplanks around the dates you met them. It's not much, but you haven't given much to go on.

-DTN
